snippet: No. 1 North Carolina and No. 2 Princeton will meet in the N.C.A.A. final Sunday.
abstract: North Carolina field hockey team defeats Syracuse, 6-1, as Princeton defeats Maryland, 3-2, in overtime; two teams will meet in the NCAA final.
